{
    "text": "The Fairytale \u2764  When I woke up yesterday I took a look outside the window and saw that everything was white white white and it was still snowing so much. \ud83d\ude0d  Everything was so beautiful.   At first I did not want to go out, because its way too early in the morning, I am tired and comfortable on the couch haha, but then I thought to myself: you will regret it of you don\u2019t, because this may very well be the last time it snows this much until the next winter.   Put on your clothes, take the camera, get in the car and head to town! And I was on my way\ud83d\ude00  Once I arrived and saw this view, I was completely amazed. The only thing I thought was: Im so glad I came. This is way too beautiful to miss. Then I moved on to lots of other beautiful places that I will share within the days with you guys!   Anteaters hope you guys like this one and let me know in the comment what you think of it.   \u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796\u2796 \u25aa \u25aa #sonya7riv #sonyphoto #summer #session #photooftheday #photosession #snowing #sweden #cameragear #photography #portrait #foto #sonyalpha #studio #stockholm #love #photo #sweden #picture #moments #momentsofmine #wintervibes #instagrammer #tamron #longexpoelite #europe #visitstockholm #myview #winterwonderland #travelphotography",
